 Stargate Game is finally.....

Yup.

Today we got our very own lovely cease and desist order from MGM. After 3 years of doing ****all and not replying to my emails there suddenly noticing us and stopping us.

I should be flattered. But im anything but.

This is purely to protect there own Stargate game which has been a rumour for awhile but i believe it will happen. Why else would you suddenly care that people are promoting your show and making others interested in the Stargate idea.

So the question is whereto from here. In the document it mentions we are not allowed to create a game based of SG1. Yet all other stargate mods get no warnings e.t.c (Ive spoken to Elite Force Stargate mod who confirms he hasnt had any desist orders).


I must say i wasnt expecting MGM to be such arseholes about the whole thing. Maybe they feel threatened over there own Stargate game?

Do we change the name ?

Do we change the game ?

Whats your thoughts ?
